Managed Account PlatformsCapital Wealth Planning is an SEC fee-based Registered Investment Advisory firm. We specialize in managing discretionary strategies that are available to institutional wealth management platforms through separately managed account solutions. Currently, our investment strategies are managed at the following regional broker-dealers and institutional wire house SMA platforms. To get additional information on the platform and strategies available, click on your firm.



























































































