Press Releases



Kevin Simpson - Capital Wealth Planning, LLC Chosen as the Best Fee-Only Investment Advisory Firm - Florida






Mar 9, 2017, 2:00pm EST














NAPLES, Fla., March 9, 2017 /PRNewswire/ --The expert senior judging panel of the 2016 Business Excellence Awards has recognized Capital Wealth Planning, LLC as the:   
Best Institutional Money Manager - Florida
The in-depth and rigorous research process, carried out by Wealth & Finance's dedicated in-house award committee, took over 6 months, during which time they counted and researched votes, analyzed all supporting evidence and performed additional interviews to ensure that only the most deserving and top performing individuals, firms and products were recognized.  
This prestigious award officially recognizes CWP as one of the most outstanding investment fee-only advisory firms in the country.  
Wealth & Finance Magazine Announces  2016 Alternative Investment Awards Winners 
The 2016 Business Excellence Awards are all about identifying and honoring the most respected companies.  They focus on the most innovative, forward thinking and client-friendly businesses that have done incredible things to influence and improve the ways in which people invest in options, art, fine wine, property, metals or any other forms of alternative commodity. Every winner is chosen on merit using a combination of votes gathered from Wealth & Finance's network of respected industry partners and the magazine's own rigorous in-house research.   
To view the complete list, please visit:  
www.wealthandfinance-intl.com/alternative-investment-awards 


NOTES FOR EDITORS 
About Capital Wealth Planning 
Capital Wealth Planning is a fee-only Investment Advisory Firm based in Naples, Florida.  The firm has been building and managing proprietary income-oriented portfolios since 2005.  CWP exists at the forefront of implementing covered call strategies with their ETF Income Portfolio, Enhanced Dividend Portfolio and Covered Call Overlay Service.  The methodologies are designed to enhance risk-adjusted returns and offer portfolio protection while delivering monthly cash-flow.  
Account inquiries should be directed to Kevin Simpson at 239-593-2100 or ksimpson@capitalwealthplanning.com.  For additional information, please visit www.capitalwealthplanning.com.   
About Wealth & Finance International 
Wealth & Finance International is a monthly publication dedicated to delivering high quality informative and up-to-the-minute global business content. It is published by AI Global Media Ltd, a publishing house that has reinvigorated corporate finance news and reporting. 
Developed by a highly skilled team of writers, editors, business insiders and regional industry experts, Wealth & Finance International reports from every corner of the globe to give readers the inside track on the need-to-know news and issues affecting banking, finance, regulation, risk and wealth management in their region. 


